ActionButton flags
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Gadget:	<ActionButton=>actionbox>
#Line
#Wrap off
Bits:	0	- Set means this is the Default action button.
	1	- Set means this is the Cancel action button.
	2	- Set means this is a local action button.
	3	- Set means that 'click show' object will be shown transiently.

Constants:
	<ActionButton_IsDefault>
	<ActionButton_IsCancel>
	<ActionButton_IsLocal>
	<ActionButton_ClickShowTransient>
	<ActionButton_ClickShowCentred>
	<ActionButton_ClickShowAtPointer>
	<ActionButton_Selected_Adjust>
	<ActionButton_Selected_Select>
	<ActionButton_Selected_Default>
	<ActionButton_Selected_Cancel>
	<ActionButton_Selected_Local>
	<ActionButton_SetClickShow_Transient>
	<ActionButton_SetClickShow_Centred>
	<ActionButton_SetClickShow_AtPointer>
	<ActionButton_GetClickShow_Transient>
	<ActionButton_GetClickShow_Centred>
	<ActionButton_GetClickShow_AtPointer>
#Line
To be used with <gadget_set_flags> & <gadget_get_flags>.
